            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            8个“不要”！体制内保持健康心态的秘诀          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                      北路                                  </span>                                                              <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                湖边看世界              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">湖边看世界</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">fo_gushi</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">湖边看世界，世界在湖边。聊聊体制内那些事，关注官场新生态。 关心官场就是关心自己。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>            <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                      </div>                                        <div id="js_tags" class="article-tag__list" style="display: none;" data-len="0">                                        <div class="article-tag-card__title">收录于合集</div>              <div class="article-tags">                              </div>                      </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.5685185185185185" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/U5fBOaXlIQnBxurdUGRVGJDO2xBsUoBBxErhibeCTwyIQUXfLVhFHfZRblicJQajx7DJ8sWqAoC1IuNmI3ZKjgCg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080"></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">很多人在工作中会面临各种各样的困难和挑战，比如工作压力大、竞争激烈、人际关系复杂、工作效率低下等。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这些问题都会影响我们的心情和状态，让我们感到焦虑、沮丧、烦躁、无力。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">如果我们不能及时调整自己的心态，就会导致身心健康受损，甚至影响我们的事业和生活。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">那么，我们应该如何在职场中保持健康的心态呢？</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">其实，并没有什么复杂的秘诀，只要我们遵循以下几个原则，就可以让自己在工作中更加轻松和快乐。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);">01<br>不要加入内卷</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">内卷是指在一个竞争激烈的环境中，为了争夺有限的资源和机会，不断提高自己的标准和要求，从而陷入一个恶性循环的现象。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">内卷不仅会消耗我们的时间和精力，还会让我们失去自己的目标和方向，降低我们的幸福感和满足感。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">所以，我们要避免加入内卷，而是要找到自己真正想要的东西，根据自己的能力和条件，制定合理的目标和计划，不要盲目跟风或者攀比，做好自己该做的事情。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);">02<br>不要责任心过剩</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">责任心是一种美德，它可以让我们更加认真负责地完成自己的工作。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">但是，如果责任心过剩，就会让我们承担过多的压力和负担，甚至牺牲自己的利益和健康。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">所以，我们要适度地担当责任，在完成自己该完成的工作之外，不要大包大揽。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">对于不属于自己范围或者超出自己能力的事情，要学会拒绝和分配。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">同时，在工作之余，也要给自己一些休息和放松的时间，不要让工作占据了自己生活的全部。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);">03<br>不要把同事当朋友</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">同事是我们在工作中最常见最密切的人际关系之一。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">与同事保持良好的关系可以让我们在工作中更加顺利和愉快。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">但是，并不是所有的同事都能成为朋友。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">有些同事可能会有不同的价值观或者利益诉求，甚至会成为我们的竞争对手或者敌人。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">所以，在与同事相处的时候，我们要保持适当的距离和礼貌，尊重别人也尊重自己。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">不要过分地交流自己的私事或者情感，避免给自己带来不必要的麻烦或者伤害。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);">04<br>不要太在意他人的评价</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">在职场中，我们难免会受到他人的评价或者评判，无论是领导、同事、客户还是其他相关人士。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这些评价或者评判可能是正面的，也可能是负面的。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">对于正面的评价，我们可以接受并感谢，但不要骄傲或者沾沾自喜。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">对于负面的评价，我们可以借鉴并改进，但不要自卑或者气馁。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">我们要明白，他人的评价或者评判，并不代表我们的真实水平或者价值，也不会影响我们的自信或者快乐。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">我们只需要做好自己，相信自己，活出自己。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);">05<br>不要害怕拒绝</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">拒绝是一种能力，也是一种权利。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">在职场中，我们可能会遇到一些不合理或者不合适的要求或者邀请，比如加班、加工、加任务、加餐等。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">如果我们不想接受这些要求或者邀请，就要勇敢地说出拒绝。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">拒绝并不意味着我们不合作或者不友好，而是意味着我们有自己的原则和底线，有自己的选择和判断。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">拒绝可以让我们保护自己的利益和健康，也可以让我们节省时间和精力，提高效率和质量。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);">06<br>不要因工作而焦虑</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">焦虑是一种常见的情绪反应，它可以让我们更加警惕和努力地面对困难和挑战。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">但是，如果焦虑过度，就会让我们失去理智和平衡，影响我们的思维和行为。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">所以，在工作中，我们要避免因工作而焦虑。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">当我们遇到一些困难或者挑战的时候，我们要冷静地分析和解决，而不是慌乱地逃避或者抵抗。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">当我们感到压力或者紧张的时候，我们要及时地放松和调节，而不是一味地压抑或者发泄。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);">07<br>不要太出风头</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">出风头是指在一个群体中过分地表现自己的能力或者优势，从而引起他人的注意或者羡慕。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">出风头有时候可以让我们获得一些赞誉或者机会，但也可能会让我们招致一些嫉妒或者敌意。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">所以，在体制内职场中，我们要适度地出风头。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">在工作中，我们要高效地完成自己的任务，并积极地展示自己的成果和贡献。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">但是，在与人交往中，我们要低调地表现自己，并谦虚地接受他人的建议和帮助。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);">08<br>不要把情绪带到生活中</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "PingFang SC";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">工作是工作，生活是生活！</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "PingFang SC";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">不要将工作时的不愉快延伸到生活，影响自己的心情。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "PingFang SC";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">工作的时候你只是一部运转的机器，下班的生活才是灵魂回归肉体的高光时刻。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "PingFang SC";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">所以，在生活中要学会享受和感恩，和家人朋友多沟通和交流，给自己一些温暖和快乐。</span></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="6479251" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>              </div>    </div>]]></description>
